# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_MAX_BRAKING

## Summary
Get the maximum braking force this vehicle (with mods) can apply, may not be accurate due to tyres slipping

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle: Index - vehicle of interest

## Returns
* **FLOAT**
